 Inglaterra","All Hallows church, London, Midlesex,England":"Allhallows, Cumberland, Inglaterra, United Kingdom","Wishou, Nottinghamahsire,England":"Inglaterra, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"John Lovetot the Elder nasceu em 1235, em Inglaterra, United Kingdom. Ele casou-se com Margaret d'Eiville em janeiro de 1268. Eles tiveram pelo menos 3 filhos e 3 filhas. Em 1275, sua profissão aparece como knight of justice of common pleas. Ele faleceu em 5 de novembro de 1294, com 59 anos, e foi sepultado em Allhallows, Cumberland, Inglaterra, United Kingdom."},"ro":{"1235–5 November 1294":"1235–5 noiembrie 1294","1239–1290":"1239–1290","–1302":"–1302","1260–1319":"1260–1319","–1294":"–1294","–1303":"–1303","–Female":"Decedată","–Male":"Decedat","1235–1294":"1235–1294","1294":"1294","1260":"1260","from 1275 to 1289":"din 1275 până în 1289","November 1294":"noiembrie 1294","1290":"1290","1239":"1239","1303":"1303","1302":"1302","1235":"1235","by 1268  1st wife":"ianuarie 1268","5 November 1294":"5 noiembrie 1294","1319":"1319","aft 1290  2nd wife  2nd husband":"după 2 februarie 1290","Kenardington, Kent, England":"Kenardington, Kent, England","All Hallows church, London, Midlesex,England":"Allhallows, Cumberland, Anglia, United Kingdom","Wishou, Nottinghamahsire,England":"Anglia, United Kingdom"},"ru":{"1235–5 November 1294":"1235 г.–5 ноября 1294 г.","1239–1290":"1239г.–1290г.","–1302":"–1302г.","1260–1319":"1260г.–1319г.","–1294":"–1294г.","–1303":"–1303г.","–Female":"Умершая","–Male":"Умерший","1235–1294":"1235г.–1294г.","1294":"1294 г.","1260":"1260 г.","from 1275 to 1289":"с 1275 по 1289","November 1294":"ноябрь 1294 г.","1290":"1290 г.","1239":"1239 г.","1303":"1303 г.","1302":"1302 г.","1235":"1235 г.","by 1268  1st wife":"январь 1268 г.","5 November 1294":"5 ноября 1294 г.","1319":"1319 г.","aft 1290  2nd wife  2nd husband":"после 2 февраль 1290 г.","Kenardington, Kent, England":"кенардингтон, кэнт, Англия","All Hallows church, London, Midlesex,England":"аллхоллоус, ку